Title: Phone number field in update section accepts any digit phone number.

Description: When i enter any digit more than 10 in input field then input field accepts it.

Steps to reproduce: Go to "My Account" in the navigation bar then go to "My Addresses" then click on "Update"
and put values in home phone input field. 

Environment: Google Chrome

Expected results: A phone number must be 10 digit numeric value.

